 (Reuters) - Chrysler LLC reports July 2009 U.S. sales increases 

 Highlights: * Chrysler Group LLC reports July 2009 U.S. sales increases * Chrysler Group LLC total sales up 30 percent compared with previous month * Chrysler Group LLC says inventory is down 68 percent versus June 2008 * Chrysler Group says total U.S. sales for July 2009 of 88,900 units * Says will offer 0 percent financing for up to 72 months through GMAC financial services on select 2009 model vehicles * Incentives are valid through August 31, 2009